org.ahocorasick.trie

类 PayloadTrie<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ahocorasick.trie.PayloadTrie<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - The type of the supplied of the payload.

    public class PayloadTrie<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A trie implementation that carries a payload. See Trie for details on usage.

    The payload trie adds the possibility to specify emitted payloads for each added keyword.

    作者:
    Daniel Beck
